text: Lyubov Kochetova (born 7 May 1982) is a Russian equestrian. She competed in the individual jumping event at the 2008 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1982 births Category:Living people Category:Russian female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Russia Category:Equestrians at the 2008 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Leningrad Oblast
